Just Steps

Install Cloudinary SDK: npm install cloudinary.

Set up Cloudinary with your credentials in cloudinaryConfig.js.

Create a simple Express server that handles image uploads.

Use Multer for file handling in memory.

Upload images to Cloudinary and get the URL.

Test the upload and view the image on the Cloudinary Dashboard.